Every song is a 50 song ... do not play this at your 3 year old's birthday party

Like all mixtapes .... there are too many DJ announcements and affects

Bob fans ... it sounds a LOT less like Bob than you might think ... there are no Bob/50 duets or anything even remotely like that.
